fields.name: Sole NEW TT8 Treadmill AC
fields.description: The Sole TT8 treadmill offers uncompromising quality for years of use, performing at the same level as – and is comparable to – commercial models at a higher price point. Features include a 22” wide running surface, 15 levels of incline, 6 levels of decline and a 10.1” graphic display.

fields.name: Life Fitness T3 Treadmill
fields.description: Stylish curves and high quality comfort features make the T3 ideal for the home. Features a powerful motor with a top speed of 19km/h and FlexDeck® shock absorption. The Go console includes all the programming you need to get started!

fields.name: ProForm 305 CST Folding Treadmill
fields.description: Powered by a 2.0 CHP Motor, the ProForm 305 CST Folding Treadmill features a Rebound Cushioning system, digital speed and incline controls, 10 pre-set workouts and a folding frame for those short on space.

fields.name: ProForm Trainer 8.5 Folding Treadmill
fields.description: Ideal for comfortable and motivational home cardio training, the ProForm Trainer 8.5 Folding Treadmill comes equipped with a 2.6 CHP motor, ProShox™ cushioning system, 0 – 10% Quick Incline™, a 16 kph top speed and a 5” high contrast multi-colour display.

fields.name: Kettler Cycle M Exercise Bike
fields.description: A great space-saving option for home gym-goers, the Kettler Cycle M exercise bike delivers a smooth ride in the comfort of your own home. Features include 8 stages of resistance, vertical seat adjustments and a 6kg flywheel.

fields.name: Kettler Giro C3 Exercise Cycle
fields.description: Get your cardio routine underway in the comfort of your own home with the Kettler Giro C3 Exercise Bike, featuring 10 built-in workout programmes, 15 magnetic resistance levels, an adjustable seat and a tablet holder too.

fields.name: BH Fitness I.Artic Upright Cycle with Bluetooth
fields.description: Enjoy a smoother cardio session with the I.Artic Upright Cycle – featuring 9 pre-set programmes, an M2 Classic monitor with a dual backlit display, an XXL saddle, and iConcept with Bluetooth 4.0 technology.

fields.name: ProForm 8.0 EX Upright Bike
fields.description: Delivering a comfortable home cycling session, the ProForm 8.0 EX Upright Bike features 30 pre-set workout apps, 25 levels of Digital QuickResistance®, a 5” backlit display and more!

fields.name: Kettler Cross M Elliptical Cross Trainer
fields.description: Ideal for beginners and cardio fans that just want to get moving quickly, the Kettler Cross M Elliptical Cross Trainer is fitted with a 12kg rear flywheel, a magnetic brake system that delivers 8 stages of resistance and a 15-inch stride length with adjustable treads.

fields.name: BH Fitness MYCRON C170 Cross Trainer
fields.description: Ideal for regular use in any home gym environment, the BH Fitness Mycron C170 Cross Trainer features 24 intensity levels, a 43.5cm stride, Bluetooth and telemetric heart rate monitoring, 12 pre-set programmes and iConcept for access to your favourite fitness apps.

fields.name: ProForm SE Elliptical Cross Trainer
fields.description: Featuring SMR™ Silent Magnetic Resistance, a 10kg inertia enhanced flywheel, 41 cm stride length and adjustable ergo path, the ProForm SE Elliptical is perfect for both beginners and experienced exercisers.

fields.name: ProForm Hybrid Trainer XT
fields.description: Experience the ultimate cardio combination with ProForm’s Hybrid Trainer. Featuring a 38 cm stride length, SMR™ Silent Magnetic Resistance and Inertia Enhanced Flywheel, this elliptical/cycle hybrid is perfect for any fitness fanatic.

fields.name: Body-Solid R300 Endurance Rowing Machine
fields.description: Delivering an effective low-impact cardio and total body workout, the Endurance R300 Air Rower is a high performance machine. Featuring an interactive console, user-controlled air resistance, precisions-engineered flywheel and 8 different exercise programmes.

fields.name: Concept2 RowErg w/Standard Legs (Black)
fields.description: The durable Concept2 RowErg (formerly known as the Model D) is a great value, high performance rowing machine. Featuring the most advanced PM5 console, it offers accurate workout tracking, pre-set programmes and ANT+ and Bluetooth Smart connectivity. *Folding design*

fields.name: NordicTrack RW600 Rowing Machine
fields.description: Stream high-energy rowing classes in the comfort of your own home, boost your physical and mental strength with two forms of resistance and enjoy limitless training variety with the free 30 day iFit Family subscription, all on the new NordicTrack RW600 Rower.

fields.name: ProForm Carbon R10 Rowing Machine
fields.description: Bring the full rowing experience home with the ProForm Carbon R10 Rower. Standout features include a 10” Smart HD Touchscreen, 24 digital resistance levels, ergonomic touchpoints and a space-saving folding frame.

fields.name: Body Power 20Kg Spinlock Dumbbell Weight Set
fields.description: Featuring various weight plates, chrome spinlock collars and solid chrome spinlock bars, the easily adjustable Body Power 20kg Spinlock Dumbbell Set is ideal for beginners.

fields.name: Body Power 37kg Tri-Grip Vinyl Weight Set
fields.description: The perfect weight training set for home use. Body Power 37kg Tri-Grip Vinyl Weight Set comprises a compact 5ft Hollow Standard barbell, two Spinlock Dumbbells and 35kg of Tri-Grip Vinyl Weight Discs. 6 x Spinlock collars included.

fields.name: Body Power 32kg Tri-Grip Vinyl Weight Set with 2 Piece Bar
fields.description: The 32kg Tri-Grip Vinyl Weight set includes a 5ft 2 Piece tubular standard spinlock bar that is perfect for strength building.

fields.name: Body Power XD100 PU Bag Gloves - Small
fields.description: Perfect for pounding the punch bag, these high quality PU Bag Gloves feature protective moulded foam inserts, non-slip lining and ventilated palms. Fully adjustable. Size Small.

fields.name: Boxing-Mad Leather Pro Sparring Gloves 8 oz
fields.description: Boxing-Mad Leather Pro Sparring Gloves 8 oz

fields.name: Body Power 55cm Gym Ball With Pump
fields.description: Suitable for a wide range of core, strength, flexibility, preparation and recovery exercises, the Body Power Gym Ball is a must have piece of fitness equipment. Size: 55cm – pump included.

fields.name: Body Power 75cm Gym Ball With Pump
fields.description: Suitable for a wide range of core, strength, flexibility, preparation and recovery exercises, the Body Power Gym Ball is a must have piece of fitness equipment. Size: 75cm – pump included.

fields.name: Reebok Step
fields.description: Ideal for home gyms and studio workout environments, the Reebok Step is the perfect HIIT companion. Height adjustable, users can customise the intensity of workouts, and store it away easily.
